<subSubSection id="A7CC2DBDFFCDFFE6FF8DFD44FE03FBA9" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFCDFFE6FF8DFD44FDB8FC09" blockId="23.[113,1089,674,1081]" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FF8DFD44FF5EFD09" bold="true" box="[113,224,674,697]" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFCDFFE6FF19FD44FEC2FD09" author="SPAETH" box="[229,380,674,697]" firstAuthor="SPAETH" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" pagination="135 - 158" refId="ref51390" refString="SPAETH F. 1937: Neue Cassidinen des Rijksmuseums in Leiden und meiner Sammlung. Temminckia 2: 135 - 158." type="journal article" year="1937">SPAETH (1937)</bibRefCitation>
reduced 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FE20FD44FC2AFD09" authority="(Boheman, 1855)" baseAuthorityName="Boheman" baseAuthorityYear="1855" box="[476,916,674,697]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Plagiometriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moesta">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FE20FD44FD6BFD09" box="[476,725,674,697]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">Plagiometriona moesta</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFCDFFE6FD1DFD44FC33FD09" author="Boheman" box="[737,909,674,697]" firstAuthor="Boheman" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" refId="ref47955" refString="BOHEMAN C. H. 1855: Monographia Cassididarum. Tomus Tertius. Officina Norstedtiana, Holmiae, 543 pp. + 1 pl." type="book" year="1855">Boheman, 1855</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
as an aberration of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FF6CFD24FF42FD69" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[144,252,706,729]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="buqueti">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FF6CFD24FF42FD69" box="[144,252,706,729]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. buqueti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, probably based on the primary description. Since then the former taxon has been considered as synonym of the latter (see 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFCDFFE6FD9BFD04FCA2FD49" author="BOROWIEC" box="[615,796,738,761]" firstAuthor="BOROWIEC" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" refId="ref48283" refString="BOROWIEC L. 1999 a: A world catalogue of the Cassidinae (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae). Biologica Silesiae, Wroclaw, 476 pp." type="book" year="1999" yearSuffix="a">BOROWIEC 1999a</bibRefCitation>
). According to the primary description 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFCDFFE6FF0DFCE4FE18FCA9" author="BOHEMAN" box="[241,422,770,793]" firstAuthor="BOHEMAN" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" refId="ref47955" refString="BOHEMAN C. H. 1855: Monographia Cassididarum. Tomus Tertius. Officina Norstedtiana, Holmiae, 543 pp. + 1 pl." type="book" year="1855">BOHEMAN (1855)</bibRefCitation>
compared 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FDDEFCE4FD35FCA9" baseAuthorityName="Boheman" baseAuthorityYear="1855" box="[546,651,770,793]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Plagiometriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moesta">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FDDEFCE4FD35FCA9" box="[546,651,770,793]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. moesta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FD4EFCE4FCA1FCA9" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[690,799,770,793]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="buqueti">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FD4EFCE4FCA1FCA9" box="[690,799,770,793]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. buqueti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and mentioned that it has acutely pointed humeral angles and yellow elytra with a large black spot reaching far beyond the middle of elytra. Although many species of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FD9CFCA4FCB9FCE9" authorityName="Spaeth" authorityYear="1899" box="[608,775,834,857]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Plagiometriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FD9CFCA4FCB9FCE9" box="[608,775,834,857]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">Plagiometriona</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
display significant variability in the dorsal colour pattern (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFCDFFE6FE30FC84FD37FCC9" author="FLINTE" box="[460,649,866,889]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="FLINTE" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" pagination="891 - 904" refId="ref49364" refString="FLINTE V., WINDSOR D., SEKERKA L., MACEDO M. V. &amp; MONTEIRO R. F. 2010: Plagiometriona emarcida (Boheman, 1855) and Plagiometriona forcipata (Boheman, 1855) (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Cassidinae), a single species differing in larval performance and adult phenotype. Journal of Natural History 44: 891 - 904." type="journal article" year="2010">FLINTE et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FD60FC84FCBBFCC9" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[668,773,866,889]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="buqueti">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FD60FC84FCBBFCC9" box="[668,773,866,889]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. buqueti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
belongs to a group of species with fairly constant elytral pattern. Therefore it is desirable to study the 
<typeStatus id="306DC094FFCDFFE6FC93FC64FC23FC29" box="[879,925,898,921]" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FC3CFC64FB98FC29" baseAuthorityName="Boheman" baseAuthorityYear="1855" box="[960,1062,898,921]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Plagiometriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moesta">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FC3CFC64FB98FC29" box="[960,1062,898,921]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. moesta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to verify whether the synonymy is valid.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFCDFFE6FF6CFC24FE03FBA9" blockId="23.[113,1089,674,1081]" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">
The distribution is given according to 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFCDFFE6FDD0FC24FD5FFC69" author="WAGENER" box="[556,737,962,985]" firstAuthor="WAGENER" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" pagination="49 - 79" refId="ref52211" refString="WAGENER B. 1877: Cassididae. Mittheilungen des Munchner Entomologischen Vereins 1: 49 - 79." type="journal article" year="1877">WAGENER (1877)</bibRefCitation>
, who published several faunistic records of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FF19FC04FEF1FC49" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[229,335,994,1017]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="buqueti">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FF19FC04FEF1FC49" box="[229,335,994,1017]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. buqueti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="97C13EA6FFCDFFE6FE6EFC04FE41FC49" box="[402,511,994,1017]" name="Colombia" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">Colombia</collectingCountry>
. It is necessary to verify respective specimens as they might also belong to 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFCDFFE6FEAFFBE4FE08FBA9" baseAuthorityName="Boheman" baseAuthorityYear="1855" box="[339,438,1026,1049]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Plagiometriona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="298" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bremei">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFCDFFE6FEAFFBE4FE08FBA9" box="[339,438,1026,1049]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="298">P. bremei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
